{"word":"βαρύτης","slug":"βαρύτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βαρύτης</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βαρύς'><el>βαρύς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>weight, heaviness</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of men, <i>importunity, disagreeableness</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>in good sense, <i>gravity, dignity</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b>of sound, <i>strength, depth</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}